OL,3,CProposal to fine drivers of illegal
OL,4,C'Facebook lifts'
OL,6,FJersey residents offering illegal taxi
OL,7,Flifts for money could face fines of up
OL,8,Fto #10,000 under a proposed legal
OL,9,Fcrackdown.
OL,11,FDeputy Catherine Curtis wants to
OL,12,Fupdate the Motor Traffic (Jersey) Law
OL,13,F1935 to enable the prosecution of
OL,14,Fillegal taxi services.
OL,16,FHer proposal could make anyone
OL,17,Fadvertising an unlicensed lift subject
OL,18,Fto a Level Three fine - up to #10,000.
OL,19,FOffering payment for a lift would also
OL,20,Fbe a criminal offence liable to a
OL,21,FLevel Two fine.
