OL,3,CProposal to fine drivers of illegal
OL,4,C'Facebook lifts'
OL,6,FIf approved, the legislation would
OL,7,Fcome into force before 31st March 2027.
OL,9,FThe proposition aims to crack down on
OL,10,Fa rise in unlicensed taxi drivers, who
OL,11,Fusually offer lifts through Facebook
OL,12,Fgroups such as 'Jersey lifts'.
OL,14,FThe current Motor Traffic law defines
OL,15,Fwhat can be classed as a taxi and the
OL,16,Fnumber of licensed taxis allowed to
OL,17,Foperate on the island.
