OL,3,CProposal to fine drivers of illegal
OL,4,C'Facebook lifts'
OL,6,FWhile strict conditions on issuing
OL,7,Flicences for vehicles and drivers are
OL,8,Fin place, it does not adequately allow
OL,9,Ffor effective prosecutions for those
OL,10,Foperating an unregulated taxi service.
OL,12,FDeputy Catherine Curtis told ITV News
OL,13,Fthat the rise of illegal rides has
OL,14,F"really got out of hand", and has gone
OL,15,Ffurther than just offering lift shares.
