OL,3,CProposal to fine drivers of illegal
OL,4,C'Facebook lifts'
OL,6,F"People are earning their living from
OL,7,Fit. They're not paying tax or social
OL,8,Fsecurity, they're not insured, and
OL,9,Fthey haven't had DBS checks, so you
OL,10,Fcould be getting a lift from anyone,"
OL,11,FDeputy Curtis explained.
OL,13,F"Taxi drivers have to meet various
OL,14,Fstandards, including customer care and
OL,15,Fdisability awareness - their cars are
OL,16,Fchecked once a year for safety, and
OL,17,Fare expensively insured to cover any
OL,18,Faccidents."
