OL,3,CProposal to fine drivers of illegal
OL,4,C'Facebook lifts'
OL,6,FQuestions remain about how police
OL,7,Fwould enforce any update to the law,
OL,8,Fand differentiate between a
OL,9,F'professional' lift-giver and someone
OL,10,Fhaving their petrol costs covered on a
OL,11,Ftrip with their friends.
OL,13,FIn response, Deputy Curtis said,
OL,14,F"There will be ways to prove that
OL,15,Fpeople are offering an illegal taxi
OL,16,Fservice, especially after an accident.
OL,18,F"There will be proof of payment
OL,19,Fthrough the phone or on social media."
